members.name: AnimationPlaybackEvent.AnimationPlaybackEvent()
members.description: Constructs a new AnimationPlaybackEvent object instance.

parameters.name: type
parameters.description: A DOMString representing the name of the event.

parameters.name: eventInitDict Optional
parameters.description: An optional EventInit dictionary object containing the following fields: bubbles Optional Defaults to false, of type Boolean, indicating if the event bubbles or not. cancelable Optional Defaults to false, of type Boolean, indicating if the event can be canceled or not. detail Optional Defaults to null, of type any — an event-dependent value associated with the event.

parameters.name: bubbles Optional
parameters.description: Defaults to false, of type Boolean, indicating if the event bubbles or not.

parameters.name: cancelable Optional
parameters.description: Defaults to false, of type Boolean, indicating if the event can be canceled or not.

parameters.name: detail Optional
parameters.description: Defaults to null, of type any — an event-dependent value associated with the event.

members.name: AnimationPlaybackEvent.currentTime
members.description: The current time of the animation that generated the event.

members.name: AnimationPlaybackEvent.timelineTime
members.description: The time value of the timeline of the animation that generated the event.
